cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE. 

The paper deals with cross-language adaptation for question-question similarity reranking in community question answering, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Additionally, the use of adversarial training of neural networks (GANs) is a key aspect of the paper, which falls under the sub-category of neural networks (cs.NE).
